        Transfer Duty Concessions in Queensland: What Downsizers and Seniors Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Transfer duty can add tens of thousands of dollars to the cost of buying your next home. Understanding what concessions exist in Queensland, and what does not, is important before you plan your next move.
      </p>
